from nltk.tokenize import word_tokenize, sent_tokenize
In [31]:
def word_count(sent):
    wc = word_tokenize(sent)
    return len(wc)
In [32]:
df['Text_Word_Count'] = df['Text'].apply(word_count)

    return len(sc)
